WEBVTT

00:00:01.670 --> 00:00:03.470
You came alone without a lawyer.

00:00:04.190 --> 00:00:06.520
Are you planning to hire one for the trial?

00:00:07.010 --> 00:00:11.890
I heard you insisted on giving your statement before Oh Jahyeon.

00:00:12.280 --> 00:00:13.700
Say what you want.

00:00:13.860 --> 00:00:16.820
I stabbed Koryoin Kim with the syringe.

00:00:16.820 --> 00:00:18.680
I didn't mean to kill him.

00:00:18.820 --> 00:00:20.040
I just wanted to scare him.

00:00:20.040 --> 00:00:21.970
That wasn't just a syringe.

00:00:22.430 --> 00:00:24.930
It was one filled with pure nicotine.

00:00:25.320 --> 00:00:27.450
If you thought the dose wasn't lethal,

00:00:27.550 --> 00:00:29.550
When he collapsed,

00:00:29.680 --> 00:00:32.490
You couldn't have been sure you poisoned him.

00:00:32.700 --> 00:00:33.860
That's hard to say.

00:00:44.110 --> 00:00:45.980
The drugs were secretly swapped.

00:00:46.160 --> 00:00:50.330
The amount was already less than agreed, which was infuriating.

00:00:50.580 --> 00:00:53.240
Seems like he shamelessly demanded more money.

00:00:53.770 --> 00:00:57.060
We already found evidence of Oh Jahyeon distributing drugs.

00:00:57.060 --> 00:00:59.190
Confessing would be more beneficial—

00:00:59.220 --> 00:01:01.160
Both of us understand this.

00:01:01.300 --> 00:01:04.030
Don't waste time. Let's just make things simple.

00:01:18.530 --> 00:01:21.530
Because of this, Jahyeon rushed at that man.

00:01:21.660 --> 00:01:23.470
But that guy hit Jahyeon.

00:01:23.550 --> 00:01:24.740
So I got angry in that moment

00:01:24.740 --> 00:01:27.730
And stabbed his neck with the nicotine syringe.

00:01:27.860 --> 00:01:30.590
So you're admitting to all the charges?

00:01:32.710 --> 00:01:34.080
I admit to everything.

00:01:35.360 --> 00:01:36.860
Seven years ago,

00:01:36.990 --> 00:01:38.380
Oh Jahyeon's husband and

00:01:38.380 --> 00:01:40.979
Her regular OB-GYN, Granny Park, died, right?

00:01:41.080 --> 00:01:45.130
Two years before these incidents,

00:01:45.210 --> 00:01:47.370
Anesthetics from one of your cases went missing.

00:01:47.370 --> 00:01:51.360
Did you use those anesthetics to kill Oh Jahyeon's husband?

00:01:51.620 --> 00:01:52.900
Me?

00:01:53.580 --> 00:01:55.240
Why... would I?

00:01:55.360 --> 00:01:58.570
Records were found on Granny Park's phone.

00:02:14.620 --> 00:02:16.570
Granny Park's phone—

00:02:17.150 --> 00:02:18.480
I had the data analyzed.

00:02:18.550 --> 00:02:20.260
Nothing was found, right?

00:02:23.660 --> 00:02:26.480
I admit I had anesthetics go missing in my case before.

00:02:26.480 --> 00:02:28.260
Jahyeon's husband died of cardiac arrest.

00:02:28.260 --> 00:02:30.900
As for Granny Park, I don't know much about that.

00:02:30.900 --> 00:02:33.230
What about the casino boss, Kang Woosung?

00:02:35.700 --> 00:02:37.530
Lee Gilyoung killed him.

00:02:39.310 --> 00:02:40.470
Look up.

00:02:49.630 --> 00:02:52.410
I see you hid it in a flower pot.

00:02:52.980 --> 00:02:54.400
Your souvenir.

00:02:54.690 --> 00:02:56.690
Wow, our Taeseon has grown up.

00:02:56.840 --> 00:02:58.100
You even know to search my office.

00:02:58.100 --> 00:03:02.180
Where is the awl that stabbed the casino boss Kang Woosung's neck?

00:03:02.310 --> 00:03:03.330
Tell me the truth.

00:03:03.470 --> 00:03:06.470
I mean, how would I know?

00:03:06.620 --> 00:03:07.430
What's his name, Lee Gilyoung—

00:03:07.430 --> 00:03:09.260
Ah—he's already dead, right?

00:03:09.690 --> 00:03:12.240
I'm asking where you hid your souvenir!

00:03:15.440 --> 00:03:17.700
In his father's grave.

00:03:19.460 --> 00:03:21.470
If you keep acting like this,

00:03:21.600 --> 00:03:23.930
I'll have to take away what you care about.

00:03:25.079 --> 00:03:26.340
Don't touch Jahyeon.

00:03:30.450 --> 00:03:33.050
The DNA found in the glove, and...

00:03:33.970 --> 00:03:37.520
The burner phone ending in 1225—

00:03:38.840 --> 00:03:40.490
Who could it belong to?

00:03:51.140 --> 00:03:52.740
I don't know.

00:03:52.870 --> 00:03:54.800
The accomplice who dumped the body

00:03:54.910 --> 00:03:57.250
Is also your and Oh Jahyeon's son.

00:04:07.950 --> 00:04:09.220
Who is it?

00:04:09.420 --> 00:04:12.210
You insist on denying these two things to the end, huh?

00:04:12.210 --> 00:04:14.170
Then there's no choice—

00:04:14.240 --> 00:04:15.920
I can only find the person

00:04:16.140 --> 00:04:18.540
And put them in jail.

00:04:20.420 --> 00:04:21.790
Do whatever you want.

00:04:33.710 --> 00:04:34.980
What should we do next?

00:04:35.680 --> 00:04:36.740
What else can we do?

00:04:36.830 --> 00:04:38.760
Next, we have to face them head-on.

00:04:38.940 --> 00:04:40.730
Face them head-on?

00:04:41.260 --> 00:04:43.620
We must find a way to make them move.

00:04:46.770 --> 00:04:48.830
[Park Siwoo]

00:04:51.280 --> 00:04:54.190
[Kim Yoonsik]

00:04:59.050 --> 00:05:00.690
[Kwak Seunghwan] [Because of inheritance?]

00:05:01.270 --> 00:05:02.950
[Koryoin Mr. Kim overdosed on drugs]

00:05:03.170 --> 00:05:04.810
[Found in a small room on the second floor]

00:05:05.050 --> 00:05:07.040
[The Last Abandoned Mine in Danhyeon City To Be Turned Into a Casino]

00:05:07.600 --> 00:05:09.870
[Led by Ohsong Construction, 'Danhyeon Land' Integrated Resort (Casino, Hotel, Theme Park) to be built— Officially secures $400M in foreign investment]

00:05:10.020 --> 00:05:14.290
[Casino Industry's First Female Executive Pledges "Transparent Operations, Regional Co-Prosperity"]

00:05:14.450 --> 00:05:16.310
[Danhyeon City "Casino Owner Murdered"; the suspect is his driver, Lee]

00:05:22.720 --> 00:05:25.110
[The Prosecutor's Proposal]

00:05:25.120 --> 00:05:26.870
[Prosecutor's Office] [Room 512]

00:05:26.970 --> 00:05:30.060
I will prosecute the Koryoin case

00:05:30.210 --> 00:05:32.930
On charges of attempted murder, abandoning a corpse,

00:05:32.930 --> 00:05:35.260
And violating the Narcotics Control Act.

00:05:35.260 --> 00:05:37.290
What?

00:05:37.420 --> 00:05:38.880
Whether it's the case of the casino boss Kang Woosung

00:05:38.880 --> 00:05:40.050
Or the murder of Granny Park—

00:05:40.050 --> 00:05:42.340
We haven't found any solid evidence.

00:05:42.450 --> 00:05:44.470
Didn't you say you'd take your time to investigate before indicting?

00:05:44.470 --> 00:05:46.460
Are you suddenly proposing to indict immediately now?

00:05:46.460 --> 00:05:48.000
Hey, Prosecutor Ju.

00:05:48.210 --> 00:05:49.540
What's the rush?

00:05:49.909 --> 00:05:52.300
The remaining cases are all old cases from the past,

00:05:52.300 --> 00:05:54.230
And the evidence is insufficient.

00:05:54.320 --> 00:05:56.380
No one knows when they'll be solved.

00:05:58.390 --> 00:06:01.700
I mean we should start indicting the ones with solid evidence.

00:06:01.700 --> 00:06:04.100
It's because of Senior Assistant Lee, huh?

00:06:05.120 --> 00:06:08.850
We have to prosecute and start a public trial for at least one case first

00:06:08.850 --> 00:06:11.330
So that Senior Assistant Lee's suspension won't be prolonged.

00:06:11.330 --> 00:06:14.770
Compared to when Soyeon was around, you really haven't changed at all.

00:06:14.770 --> 00:06:16.240
Rushing forward headfirst like a bulldozer.

00:06:16.240 --> 00:06:19.690
Also, what if someone gets hurt again?

00:06:24.460 --> 00:06:25.860
Well...

00:06:27.100 --> 00:06:29.560
Any news from that orphanage from last time?

00:06:29.650 --> 00:06:32.040
Yeah, no news.

00:06:32.290 --> 00:06:34.330
What about the results of the phone data analysis?

00:06:34.330 --> 00:06:37.540
Well, the analysis of Oh Jahyeon's and Tak Sungwoong's is mostly done.

00:06:37.540 --> 00:06:41.040
What's suspicious has been extracted separately and sent to you.

00:06:41.040 --> 00:06:43.130
Things like, "The two of them seem to be still in contact,"

00:06:43.130 --> 00:06:44.310
"We must do it anyway,"

00:06:44.310 --> 00:06:47.440
[If my husband finds out about this... he will definitely tell my dad.]

00:06:44.340 --> 00:06:46.060
"If my husband finds out about this,

00:06:46.060 --> 00:06:47.450
He will definitely tell my dad."

00:06:47.450 --> 00:06:49.850
There are also concerning parts like this.

00:06:50.170 --> 00:06:52.700
But... coincidentally,

00:06:52.900 --> 00:06:55.270
Important keywords are missing.

00:06:56.100 --> 00:06:59.060
Is there anything that can be used as direct evidence?

00:06:59.060 --> 00:07:03.290
I didn't expect Director Tak to be so meticulous.

00:07:04.050 --> 00:07:07.440
The National Forensic Service sent a message this afternoon.

00:07:07.440 --> 00:07:09.890
They said that among Tak Sungwoong's seized items,

00:07:09.890 --> 00:07:12.890
It seems a piece of evidence was contaminated by the investigator.

00:07:12.890 --> 00:07:16.910
The people from the National Forensic Service said they would compare the DNA and filter it out first.

00:07:16.910 --> 00:07:19.110
Sorry, I made sure I was wearing gloves,

00:07:19.180 --> 00:07:22.220
And I also wore shoe covers.

00:07:22.350 --> 00:07:23.950
There might have been a hole.

00:07:24.590 --> 00:07:27.650
Contamination of evidence and scenes is quite common.

00:07:27.740 --> 00:07:30.410
Maybe someone else contaminated it.

00:07:30.540 --> 00:07:32.720
Prosecutor Ju and I also looked through it for a long time.

00:07:32.720 --> 00:07:34.670
But Chaeha,

00:07:34.800 --> 00:07:36.909
Today is your last day at work, right?

00:07:37.180 --> 00:07:38.450
That's right.

00:07:38.890 --> 00:07:41.360
I probably won't come tomorrow.

00:07:41.470 --> 00:07:42.800
I'll have to rely on you all.

00:07:42.800 --> 00:07:44.230
What are you saying?

00:07:44.980 --> 00:07:46.700
You work from home.

00:07:47.120 --> 00:07:48.770
I can't do without you.

00:07:48.909 --> 00:07:52.400
Wow, you're way too much.

00:07:52.870 --> 00:07:55.630
He's suspended, and you're still making him work.

00:07:55.630 --> 00:07:59.360
If I'm found working during my suspension, there might be an issue.

00:07:59.450 --> 00:08:01.460
What issue could there be?

00:08:01.480 --> 00:08:03.910
There are only four of us here.

00:08:11.160 --> 00:08:14.320
Well, then... I'll get going.

00:08:14.450 --> 00:08:15.520
Well...

00:08:15.980 --> 00:08:18.590
Today is Mr. Lee's last day at work.

00:08:19.000 --> 00:08:21.460
Shouldn't we at least have dinner together?

00:08:23.680 --> 00:08:24.600
Ah, sorry.

00:08:24.740 --> 00:08:26.540
Today is my birthday.

00:08:26.670 --> 00:08:28.060
I have plans tonight.

00:08:28.190 --> 00:08:30.260
Well, let's have it next time.

00:08:30.380 --> 00:08:32.820
I also made plans with my family.

00:08:32.970 --> 00:08:35.130
When Mr. Lee comes back to work...

00:08:35.850 --> 00:08:37.120
Prosecutor Yoon.

00:08:44.490 --> 00:08:45.470
Yeah?

00:08:45.930 --> 00:08:49.630
Why do you and Soyeon have different birthdays?

00:08:49.770 --> 00:08:52.160
Wasn't Soyeon's birthday yesterday?

00:08:53.710 --> 00:08:55.110
You didn't know?

00:08:55.280 --> 00:08:58.050
Soyeon and I were born 10 minutes apart, so our birthdays are different.

00:08:58.050 --> 00:09:00.300
Soyeon was born at 11:55 PM

00:09:00.460 --> 00:09:03.300
And I was born at 12:05 AM the next day.

00:09:04.100 --> 00:09:06.080
-I'm leaving. -Okay.

00:09:12.310 --> 00:09:14.560
Just stay at home.

00:09:14.880 --> 00:09:16.820
Since they've felt the pressure,

00:09:16.950 --> 00:09:20.660
I think everyone will start making a move again.

00:09:21.270 --> 00:09:25.650
Do Prosecutor Yoon Gyuho and Prosecutor Yoon Soyeon look alike?

00:09:25.830 --> 00:09:28.590
No, they are fraternal twins.

00:09:28.710 --> 00:09:30.070
I see.

00:09:30.840 --> 00:09:32.870
But they are indeed siblings.

00:09:33.060 --> 00:09:35.530
Yoon Gyuho might be Tak Sungwoong's mole,

00:09:35.790 --> 00:09:37.380
But he can't be his son.

00:09:38.010 --> 00:09:40.200
Are we exaggerating our suspicions

00:09:40.340 --> 00:09:42.400
By guessing one of them is Tak Sungwoong's son?

00:09:42.400 --> 00:09:44.960
The more exaggerated the suspicion, the better.

00:09:44.960 --> 00:09:48.020
Even if I'm suspended, I'll do my best.

00:09:48.220 --> 00:09:50.680
If we dig a little deeper, we can indict them.

00:09:50.820 --> 00:09:51.840
We can do it.

00:09:54.700 --> 00:09:55.940
Is that really so?

00:09:56.100 --> 00:09:59.890
We didn't find any evidence of plotting a crime on the phone.

00:10:00.020 --> 00:10:03.270
And there's nowhere else worth applying for a search warrant.

00:10:03.270 --> 00:10:06.130
The awl must still be in the hands of those culprits.

00:10:06.150 --> 00:10:07.580
They wouldn't throw away their souvenirs.

00:10:07.580 --> 00:10:08.840
You know that.

00:10:09.080 --> 00:10:12.350
The murder weapon was last used 7 years ago.

00:10:12.550 --> 00:10:15.060
Who'd know where they hid it?

00:10:42.890 --> 00:10:44.040
What's wrong?

00:10:44.470 --> 00:10:46.070
What are you thinking about?

00:10:47.880 --> 00:10:49.420
Nothing.

00:10:50.260 --> 00:10:53.220
What does it feel like to be rejected by your parents—

00:10:53.380 --> 00:10:55.110
I was thinking about that.

00:10:55.400 --> 00:10:57.810
Are you talking about their son?

00:10:59.490 --> 00:11:02.130
You feel pity for a criminal?

00:11:02.540 --> 00:11:05.110
You've been bullied like this,

00:11:05.330 --> 00:11:07.540
Yet you still have warmth in your heart.

00:11:08.190 --> 00:11:11.190
Carrying such a stigma for a lifetime,

00:11:11.330 --> 00:11:13.730
You should be disgusted with human nature.

00:11:14.980 --> 00:11:16.580
Right?

00:11:17.630 --> 00:11:19.730
I tried hard to hate, too,

00:11:19.890 --> 00:11:21.490
But I found that even harder.

00:11:22.270 --> 00:11:24.180
I'm strange, right?

00:11:24.610 --> 00:11:25.770
No.

00:11:26.410 --> 00:11:28.140
That's a good trait of yours.

00:11:28.330 --> 00:11:30.840
Just the fact that you were suspended

00:11:30.980 --> 00:11:34.270
Makes me want to kill those higher-ups.

00:11:49.350 --> 00:11:52.190
I told you there was no need to come in.

00:12:07.470 --> 00:12:09.600
The indictment against Director Tak—

00:12:09.700 --> 00:12:12.390
You don't have to rush it for me.

00:12:12.510 --> 00:12:15.540
It's an important case for you.

00:12:16.110 --> 00:12:17.530
Not anymore.

00:12:18.400 --> 00:12:20.650
Now I have something I want to protect.

00:12:21.050 --> 00:12:23.070
Now, compared to the past,

00:12:23.660 --> 00:12:25.660
The present is more important to me.

00:12:30.450 --> 00:12:33.020
Have a good time with your family.

00:12:42.590 --> 00:12:43.960
I'll call you later.

00:13:11.430 --> 00:13:12.390
You've arrived?

00:13:12.540 --> 00:13:14.870
Senior Assistant Lee, are you at home now?

00:13:16.030 --> 00:13:17.010
[Prosecutor Yoon Gyuho]

00:13:18.190 --> 00:13:20.030
Oh, what's the matter?

00:13:20.210 --> 00:13:23.670
It's urgent. Can you come to the office now?

00:13:24.110 --> 00:13:25.870
I can go over.

00:13:26.010 --> 00:13:28.170
But I'm suspended. Is that okay?

00:13:28.290 --> 00:13:31.260
Today isn't over yet, so the suspension hasn't started, right?

00:13:31.260 --> 00:13:34.240
Then I'll get there as soon as possible.

00:13:34.760 --> 00:13:36.490
By the way, what is this about?

00:13:36.630 --> 00:13:39.950
It's about the awl stabbing case of Granny Park, the OB-GYN—

00:13:39.950 --> 00:13:41.070
An informant has appeared.

00:13:41.070 --> 00:13:43.080
They said they're heading to the prosecutor's office now.

00:13:43.080 --> 00:13:45.400
Even if I leave now, I'm afraid I'll be late.

00:13:45.400 --> 00:13:46.690
An informant?

00:13:47.040 --> 00:13:48.450
I'll be right there.

00:14:09.360 --> 00:14:10.930
Hello, Aunt.

00:14:11.350 --> 00:14:14.650
I need to go somewhere for a bit.

00:14:14.690 --> 00:14:18.130
[Haengbok Columbarium]

00:14:15.080 --> 00:14:17.360
I'll be there as soon as possible. Sorry.

00:14:22.750 --> 00:14:26.510
[Late Yoon Soyeon]

00:14:27.240 --> 00:14:30.950
Soyeon, we're almost there.

00:15:01.330 --> 00:15:02.910
Seven years ago...

00:15:03.610 --> 00:15:04.910
Seven years ago...

00:15:05.240 --> 00:15:09.970
My sister, who passed away when she was young, is here, so I come here from time to time.

00:15:20.710 --> 00:15:23.260
[Late Tak Jisuk]

00:15:21.470 --> 00:15:24.510
Because that man killed his own sister.

00:15:25.520 --> 00:15:29.210
He regularly came to observe the death anniversary,

00:15:29.340 --> 00:15:33.780
And even went as far as moving her ashes to a new columbarium.

00:15:34.180 --> 00:15:37.040
The awl must still be in the hands of those culprits.

00:15:37.170 --> 00:15:38.850
They wouldn't throw away their souvenirs.

00:15:38.850 --> 00:15:39.800
You know that.

00:15:39.980 --> 00:15:43.090
This murder weapon was last used 7 years ago.

00:15:43.400 --> 00:15:45.570
Who'd know where they hid it?

00:15:52.480 --> 00:15:54.250
What are you doing?

00:15:54.390 --> 00:15:55.610
You can't do this!

00:15:59.930 --> 00:16:01.240
Found it.

00:16:01.760 --> 00:16:03.060
The souvenir.

00:16:03.470 --> 00:16:05.470
Hey, how could you...

00:16:05.600 --> 00:16:07.000
You're crazy. This is...

00:16:17.270 --> 00:16:18.860
You are a witness.

00:16:20.330 --> 00:16:21.540
Yes.

00:16:22.050 --> 00:16:24.060
What is going on?

00:16:33.840 --> 00:16:35.480
Mr. Lee, you got here fast.

00:16:35.720 --> 00:16:37.030
Hello.

00:16:37.170 --> 00:16:38.870
Why are you here?

00:16:39.020 --> 00:16:41.740
You came after getting a message from Prosecutor Yoon, right?

00:16:41.740 --> 00:16:44.060
He said it's better to have two people present during the interrogation,

00:16:44.060 --> 00:16:46.620
So he asked me to come along to take the informant's statement.

00:16:46.620 --> 00:16:48.310
Did he tell you what the report is about?

00:16:48.310 --> 00:16:49.290
I'm not sure yet, either.

00:16:49.290 --> 00:16:50.290
Let's go quickly.

00:16:50.320 --> 00:16:51.280
Okay.

00:17:00.770 --> 00:17:01.780
Shall we take the stairs?

00:17:01.780 --> 00:17:03.130
-Shall we? -Yeah.

00:17:11.180 --> 00:17:12.230
[National Forensic Service, Kim Jinwoo]

00:17:14.819 --> 00:17:15.680
Hello, Senior.

00:17:15.819 --> 00:17:17.240
Oh, Prosecutor Ju.

00:17:17.369 --> 00:17:20.700
About Tak Sungwoong's seized evidence that was contaminated,

00:17:20.700 --> 00:17:23.569
A staff member's DNA was detected on it.

00:17:23.700 --> 00:17:26.670
Ah, sorry about that.

00:17:26.800 --> 00:17:28.660
I'll tell them to be more careful.

00:17:28.720 --> 00:17:29.990
Well,

00:17:30.020 --> 00:17:31.720
I thought it was weird only that one piece of clothing was contaminated

00:17:31.720 --> 00:17:33.810
And the rest were fine,

00:17:33.830 --> 00:17:37.270
So I ran this employee's DNA through the database.

00:17:37.780 --> 00:17:39.980
It matched a bizarre set of data.

00:17:40.260 --> 00:17:41.680
Bizarre?

00:17:41.830 --> 00:17:42.890
Yeah.

00:17:43.020 --> 00:17:46.300
You know there was a glove at the site where the Koryoin's body was dumped, right?

00:17:46.300 --> 00:17:47.730
The DNA detected on it, which showed a father-son relationship

00:17:47.730 --> 00:17:49.350
With your Chief Prosecutor—

00:17:49.480 --> 00:17:50.480
Was a match.

00:17:52.040 --> 00:17:53.190
Who is it?

00:17:53.390 --> 00:17:57.080
Well, as to who it is,

00:17:58.290 --> 00:17:59.750
They work right under you.

00:17:59.820 --> 00:18:01.350
Investigator Song Haneul.

00:18:05.720 --> 00:18:07.180
By the way, Mr. Lee.

00:18:07.550 --> 00:18:08.880
Yeah?

00:18:10.310 --> 00:18:13.040
You aren't living in the dorms right now, are you?

00:18:19.260 --> 00:18:22.390
No, I am living there.

00:18:24.600 --> 00:18:28.430
But every time I went to your place this week,

00:18:30.680 --> 00:18:32.430
You weren't home.

00:18:37.180 --> 00:18:39.680
We all have a side we want to hide, don't we?

00:18:40.330 --> 00:18:42.200
Killing a spouse— it's usually one of two things:

00:18:42.200 --> 00:18:43.580
Cheating or life insurance.

00:18:43.580 --> 00:18:45.270
To the kid,

00:18:45.400 --> 00:18:46.780
Which one is better?

00:18:48.100 --> 00:18:50.760
People like Oh Jahyeon should all be doomed.

00:18:56.980 --> 00:18:58.340
[Investigator, Lee Chaeha]

00:18:58.910 --> 00:19:01.010
Pick up the phone, Lee Chaeha.

00:19:05.350 --> 00:19:06.600
Go to the roof.

00:19:13.060 --> 00:19:14.440
Mr. Song.

00:19:22.440 --> 00:19:24.370
Doing this won't change anything.

00:19:26.310 --> 00:19:27.470
Shut up.

00:19:28.740 --> 00:19:30.310
What do you know?

00:19:33.150 --> 00:19:35.220
Go, before I kill you.

00:19:44.810 --> 00:19:49.020
Come to think of it, I haven't heard your story.

00:19:50.460 --> 00:19:52.140
Tell me about it.

00:20:15.490 --> 00:20:16.980
How does it look to you?

00:20:17.150 --> 00:20:18.510
What do you mean?

00:20:18.950 --> 00:20:20.950
Tak Sungwoong and Oh Jahyeon.

00:20:21.520 --> 00:20:23.080
Those two bastards.

00:20:23.680 --> 00:20:25.780
They are such selfish people.

00:20:26.010 --> 00:20:28.460
They mistakenly think they are in the romance of the century.

00:20:28.460 --> 00:20:29.520
They should have given up her father's inheritance

00:20:29.520 --> 00:20:31.570
And lived well together, the three of you.

00:20:31.570 --> 00:20:33.830
I find this pathetic Romeo and Juliet act

00:20:33.960 --> 00:20:35.360
Disgusting.

00:20:35.620 --> 00:20:39.620
They never took responsibility for the consequences of their actions.

00:20:41.210 --> 00:20:42.500
You're right.

00:20:42.750 --> 00:20:46.210
You're right! Damn those two scumbags.

00:20:46.640 --> 00:20:48.470
They had a child and just threw him away.

00:20:48.470 --> 00:20:51.790
And then they left me to clean up their messes.

00:20:51.980 --> 00:20:54.460
"I killed someone. Take care of it for me."

00:20:54.600 --> 00:20:56.330
"Stay by Ju Taeseon's side and get information."

00:20:56.330 --> 00:20:58.610
Damn it, am I their servant?

00:21:00.250 --> 00:21:01.160
Hey, hey.

00:21:01.310 --> 00:21:02.760
Hey, hey!

00:21:04.070 --> 00:21:08.060
We both suffered because of our scumbag parents.

00:21:08.380 --> 00:21:12.240
But why the hell do only you guys get happiness?

00:21:12.240 --> 00:21:14.700
Do you fucking look down on me, too?

00:21:17.000 --> 00:21:19.500
If this continues, it's only my life that will be ruined.

00:21:19.500 --> 00:21:21.090
Only me again.

00:21:21.230 --> 00:21:23.710
Only me again! Damn it.

00:21:26.510 --> 00:21:30.300
I can persuade Prosecutor Ju to cover up your case.

00:21:37.850 --> 00:21:39.150
No.

00:21:39.680 --> 00:21:41.010
No.

00:21:44.790 --> 00:21:46.740
Only if you die

00:21:47.100 --> 00:21:49.580
Will Prosecutor Ju stop.

00:21:50.040 --> 00:21:51.410
Jump.

00:22:04.120 --> 00:22:07.230
Prosecutor Ju will never think I committed suicide.

00:22:07.490 --> 00:22:09.120
It doesn't matter.

00:22:10.390 --> 00:22:11.800
You know it, too.

00:22:11.990 --> 00:22:15.050
Without physical evidence, it will be dropped anyway.

00:22:20.110 --> 00:22:21.850
Jump! Damn it.

00:22:35.100 --> 00:22:36.280
Damn it.

00:22:37.150 --> 00:22:38.320
You brat.

00:22:49.800 --> 00:22:51.970
Even if I fall now, it's murder.

00:22:54.610 --> 00:22:55.300
Damn it.

00:22:59.160 --> 00:23:01.070
Damn it, this won't work.

00:23:02.420 --> 00:23:03.580
Damn it!

00:23:04.940 --> 00:23:06.000
Damn it.

00:23:08.130 --> 00:23:10.580
Damn it.

00:23:15.640 --> 00:23:19.100
Damn it, you tricky bastard.

00:23:19.390 --> 00:23:20.420
Hey.

00:23:21.000 --> 00:23:23.200
You're playing with me too, aren't you?

00:23:23.700 --> 00:23:25.150
Do you look down on me that much?

00:23:25.150 --> 00:23:27.180
Bastard, I'll kill you.

00:23:29.370 --> 00:23:30.630
Lee Chaeha!

00:23:35.900 --> 00:23:37.350
Die, all of you!

00:23:58.280 --> 00:24:00.290
Chaeha, no.

00:24:00.460 --> 00:24:01.500
Wake up.

00:24:03.160 --> 00:24:05.150
Chaeha... No...

00:24:05.150 --> 00:24:06.090
Wait.

00:24:11.360 --> 00:24:11.980
Chaeha...

00:24:12.150 --> 00:24:13.030
Chaeha...

00:24:14.100 --> 00:24:17.760
My investigator was stabbed by a suspect and lost consciousness.

00:24:17.940 --> 00:24:19.860
He was stabbed deeply in the abdomen.

00:24:19.860 --> 00:24:21.700
We are on the roof of the West District Office. Please come quickly.

00:24:21.700 --> 00:24:22.870
Quick!

00:24:23.640 --> 00:24:25.030
Chaeha. No.

00:24:25.260 --> 00:24:26.180
Wake up.

00:24:26.380 --> 00:24:26.960
Chaeha.

00:24:27.030 --> 00:24:28.000
Look at me.

00:24:29.280 --> 00:24:30.470
Chaeha...

00:24:43.890 --> 00:24:45.220
I'm sorry.

00:24:47.720 --> 00:24:50.810
But don't regret anything for me.

00:24:52.950 --> 00:24:55.000
And don't be sad.

00:24:56.950 --> 00:24:58.430
I liked you.

00:24:59.770 --> 00:25:01.010
Very much.

00:25:15.670 --> 00:25:18.340
With the exposure of the corrupt bidding for Ohsong Group's casino,

00:25:18.340 --> 00:25:23.140
The past murder case of the casino boss, Mr. Kang, has taken a new turn.

00:25:23.270 --> 00:25:26.830
The newly revealed culprits are Ms. Oh, the second daughter of Ohsong Group,

00:25:26.410 --> 00:25:28.170
[Suspect revealed to be Ms. Oh, second daughter of Ohsong Group, and Mr. Tak, Chief Prosecutor of the Danhyeon City West District Prosecutors' Office]

00:25:26.990 --> 00:25:28.420
And her long-time lover,

00:25:28.180 --> 00:25:30.070
[Breaking: True Culprits in Danhyeon City Casino Boss Murder Case Unveiled]

00:25:28.430 --> 00:25:32.170
Former Chief Prosecutor Tak of Danhyeon City's West District Office.

00:25:32.170 --> 00:25:35.930
It's reported they also have a secret son.

00:25:55.700 --> 00:25:56.860
Congratulations.

00:25:57.300 --> 00:25:58.960
Congratulations to you, too.

00:25:59.440 --> 00:26:01.960
I was thinking if you refused my proposal,

00:26:02.220 --> 00:26:04.180
I would give up everything.

00:26:06.010 --> 00:26:07.580
I don't know since when,

00:26:09.250 --> 00:26:10.490
But as long as

00:26:12.030 --> 00:26:14.210
I can be with you,

00:26:14.370 --> 00:26:16.370
I feel like everything will be fine.

00:26:16.490 --> 00:26:19.960
Now, I am only grateful.

00:26:20.160 --> 00:26:22.430
Actually, since 15 years ago,

00:26:22.550 --> 00:26:25.410
I've felt like you've spent all this time with me.

00:26:27.860 --> 00:26:29.290
You've worked hard.

00:26:30.000 --> 00:26:32.750
And thank you for enduring all this.

00:26:33.110 --> 00:26:36.210
You don't know how glad I am

00:26:36.370 --> 00:26:38.700
That you didn't end up unhappy because of me.

00:26:38.700 --> 00:26:40.710
So,

00:26:41.910 --> 00:26:46.390
I'm going to make you a proposal with very good terms.

00:26:46.730 --> 00:26:47.730
Hmm?

00:26:48.310 --> 00:26:49.790
There is only one option:

00:26:49.970 --> 00:26:51.060
"Yes."

00:26:53.480 --> 00:26:54.860
Go out with me.

00:26:55.090 --> 00:26:56.270
Lee Chaeha.

00:26:57.070 --> 00:26:58.140
Wh-What?

00:26:59.950 --> 00:27:01.760
What are you talking about?

00:27:05.430 --> 00:27:06.640
What are you doing?

00:27:08.440 --> 00:27:10.630
I told you to stay close by my side.

00:27:11.900 --> 00:27:14.360
Don't even think about going anywhere else.

00:27:15.130 --> 00:27:17.840
Where on earth did you get this?

00:27:18.250 --> 00:27:20.810
That's what I want to ask.

00:27:21.090 --> 00:27:22.590
This was in your bag.

00:27:22.830 --> 00:27:23.790
What?

00:27:24.300 --> 00:27:25.940
My bag?

00:27:26.810 --> 00:27:27.870
Ah.

00:27:28.390 --> 00:27:30.580
I usually carry handcuffs with me.

00:27:30.720 --> 00:27:31.800
Why?

00:27:32.110 --> 00:27:33.510
Just in case.

00:27:33.700 --> 00:27:36.490
When I was a police, there were times I arrested criminals I bumped into.

00:27:36.490 --> 00:27:39.770
I respect all your fetishes.

00:27:39.800 --> 00:27:40.740
Hey!

00:27:40.970 --> 00:27:42.810
I told you it's not like that.

00:27:43.030 --> 00:27:46.280
What on earth even goes on in your head?

00:27:46.700 --> 00:27:47.730
You.

00:27:50.040 --> 00:27:52.170
My mind is completely filled with you.

00:28:05.120 --> 00:28:06.290
I love you,

00:28:07.130 --> 00:28:08.260
Lee Chaeha.

00:28:15.050 --> 00:28:16.110
Answer me!

00:28:16.480 --> 00:28:18.190
I did answer you.

00:28:18.460 --> 00:28:19.800
Say it.

00:28:20.480 --> 00:28:23.140
Who still says it these days? So old-fashioned.

00:28:23.260 --> 00:28:25.060
Are you throwing a tantrum at me?

00:28:31.160 --> 00:28:33.400
If you don't like it,

00:28:34.490 --> 00:28:36.750
I'll formally make you a proposal again.

00:28:37.190 --> 00:28:38.320
Lee Chaeha,

00:28:38.830 --> 00:28:40.320
Go out with me.

00:28:44.330 --> 00:28:46.850
Misfortune is like a snake.

00:28:47.100 --> 00:28:48.770
It slithers over silently,

00:28:48.900 --> 00:28:52.540
And viciously bites the ankles of those standing defenseless and still.

00:28:52.540 --> 00:28:54.550
I tried my best to look up

00:28:54.740 --> 00:28:56.460
And looked at him.

00:28:57.330 --> 00:28:59.140
Then I started to feel

00:28:59.740 --> 00:29:02.340
It's okay even if I'm swallowed by misfortune.

00:29:02.660 --> 00:29:05.020
As long as I can be with you,

00:29:05.170 --> 00:29:07.090
Be it misfortune

00:29:07.230 --> 00:29:08.950
Or happiness—

00:29:09.250 --> 00:29:11.330
I am willing to accept them all.

